overview:
In 2001, Mac.quin, a fashion designer holding the concept of British upper-class and gentleman style, created his own brand with his own team. His own clothes are made with the best material in the world, and customized for each customer. Nowadays, most of the clothes among more than 78 senior Custom clothing shops are made from the firm of Mac.quin.

In 2012, Mac.quin’s firm started the on-line sales, making more people having the chance to enjoy the customized service. They use practiced England design to show the style.Meticulous spiritshows the taste of specialized modern gentleman. Our brand is distinguished as well as graceful and fashionable. In another word, it shows a new city style of gentlemen.
